<br>
necro's, on the other hand, can-<br>
<br>
feign death<br>
harmshield<br>
root<br>
snare<br>
fear<br>
gate<br>
use pets<br>
self-succor<br>
<br>
as you can see, necromancers have a ton more options when dealing with danger than magicians do.  and that is the big difference imho between the two classes...<br>
<br>
EDIT- just read the post a few posts back about necros becoming phased out.  our upper end guild necro solo's in plane of valor, getting like 3-10% aaxp per kill.  no risk of death to him.  seems to me like he is doing just fine, whereas i have a very difficult time soloing first tier planes of power mobs...<br>
